{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|1Jn|4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Jn","chapter":4,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v11","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Jn","bookOrder":61,"chapter":4,"verse":1,"text":"Dear friends, do not believe every spirit, but test the spirits to see if they are from God, because many false prophets have gone out into the world.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Jn","bookOrder":61,"chapter":4,"verse":2,"text":"This is how you know the Spirit of God: Every spirit that confesses that Jesus Christ has come in the flesh is from God,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Jn","bookOrder":61,"chapter":4,"verse":3,"text":"but every spirit that does not confess Jesus is not from God. This is the spirit of the antichrist, which you have heard is coming; even now it is already in the world.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Jn","bookOrder":61,"chapter":4,"verse":4,"text":"You are from God, little children, and you have conquered them, because the one who is in you is greater than the one who is in the world.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Jn","bookOrder":61,"chapter":4,"verse":5,"text":"They are from the world. Therefore what they say is from the world, and the world listens to them.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Jn","bookOrder":61,"chapter":4,"verse":6,"text":"We are from God. Anyone who knows God listens to us; anyone who is not from God does not listen to us. This is how we know the Spirit of truth and the spirit of deception.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Jn","bookOrder":61,"chapter":4,"verse":7,"text":"Dear friends, let us love one another, because love is from God, and everyone who loves has been born of God and knows God.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Jn","bookOrder":61,"chapter":4,"verse":8,"text":"The one who does not love does not know God, because God is love.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Jn","bookOrder":61,"chapter":4,"verse":9,"text":"God’s love was revealed among us in this way: God sent his one and only Son into the world so that we might live through him.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Jn","bookOrder":61,"chapter":4,"verse":10,"text":"Love consists in this: not that we loved God, but that he loved us and sent his Son to be the atoning sacrifice for our sins.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Jn","bookOrder":61,"chapter":4,"verse":11,"text":"Dear friends, if God loved us in this way, we also must love one another.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Jn","bookOrder":61,"chapter":4,"verse":12,"text":"No one has ever seen God. If we love one another, God remains in us and his love is made complete in us.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Jn","bookOrder":61,"chapter":4,"verse":13,"text":"This is how we know that we remain in him and he in us: He has given us of his Spirit.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Jn","bookOrder":61,"chapter":4,"verse":14,"text":"And we have seen and we testify that the Father has sent his Son as the world’s Savior.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Jn","bookOrder":61,"chapter":4,"verse":15,"text":"Whoever confesses that Jesus is the Son of God —God remains in him and he in God.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Jn","bookOrder":61,"chapter":4,"verse":16,"text":"And we have come to know and to believe the love that God has for us.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Jn","bookOrder":61,"chapter":4,"verse":17,"text":"In this, love is made complete with us so that we may have confidence in the day of judgment, because as he is, so also are we in this world.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Jn","bookOrder":61,"chapter":4,"verse":18,"text":"There is no fear in love; instead, perfect love drives out fear, because fear involves punishment. So the one who fears is not complete in love.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:19","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Jn","bookOrder":61,"chapter":4,"verse":19,"text":"We love because he first loved us.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:20","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Jn","bookOrder":61,"chapter":4,"verse":20,"text":"If anyone says, “I love God,” and yet hates his brother or sister, he is a liar. For the person who does not love his brother or sister whom he has seen cannot love God whom he has not seen.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:21","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Jn","bookOrder":61,"chapter":4,"verse":21,"text":"And we have this command from him: The one who loves God must also love his brother and sister.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Jn","chapter":4,"paragraphStarts":[1,2,4,7,17],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"The Spirit of Truth and the Spirit of Error"},{"beforeVerse":7,"text":"Knowing God through Love"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Dear friends, do not believe every spirit, but test the spirits "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 5:21","book":"1Th","chapter":5,"verse":21,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" to see if they are from God, because many false prophets have gone out into the world."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Th 5:21","book":"1Th","chapter":5,"verse":21}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"This is how you know the Spirit of God: Every spirit that confesses that Jesus Christ has come in the flesh "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 1:14","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 2:7","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":7,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 3:3","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":3,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" is from God, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 12:3","book":"1Co","chapter":12,"verse":3,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 1:14","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":14},{"label":"Php 2:7","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":7},{"label":"Php 3:3","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":3},{"label":"1Co 12:3","book":"1Co","chapter":12,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"but every spirit that does not confess Jesus "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss read confess that Jesus has come in the flesh"},{"kind":"text","text":" is not from God. This is the spirit of the antichrist, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 2:18","book":"1Jn","chapter":2,"verse":18,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 2:22","book":"1Jn","chapter":2,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Jn 7","book":"2Jn","chapter":1,"verse":7,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" which you have heard is coming; even now it is already in the world."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Jn 2:18","book":"1Jn","chapter":2,"verse":18},{"label":"1Jn 2:22","book":"1Jn","chapter":2,"verse":22},{"label":"2Jn 7","book":"2Jn","chapter":1,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss read confess that Jesus has come in the flesh"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You are from God, little children, and you have conquered them, because the one who is in you "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:31","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":31,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 1:27","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":27,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 3:20","book":"1Jn","chapter":3,"verse":20,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" is greater than the one who is in the world. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 12:31","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":31,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 8:31","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":31},{"label":"Col 1:27","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":27},{"label":"1Jn 3:20","book":"1Jn","chapter":3,"verse":20},{"label":"Jn 12:31","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":31}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They are from the world. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 17:6","book":"Jhn","chapter":17,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Pt 2:20","book":"2Pe","chapter":2,"verse":20,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" Therefore what they say is from the world, and the world listens to them. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 17:6","book":"Jhn","chapter":17,"verse":6},{"label":"2Pt 2:20","book":"2Pe","chapter":2,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"We are from God. Anyone who knows God listens to us; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 8:47","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":47,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" anyone who is not from God does not listen to us. This is how we know the Spirit of truth and the spirit of deception. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 13:5–6","book":"Mrk","chapter":13,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 2:12","book":"1Co","chapter":2,"verse":12,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 4:1","book":"1Ti","chapter":4,"verse":1,"letter":"d"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 8:47","book":"Jhn","chapter":8,"verse":47},{"label":"Mk 13:5–6","book":"Mrk","chapter":13,"verse":5},{"label":"1Co 2:12","book":"1Co","chapter":2,"verse":12},{"label":"1Tm 4:1","book":"1Ti","chapter":4,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Dear friends, let us love one another, because love is from God, and everyone who loves has been born of God "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 2:29","book":"1Jn","chapter":2,"verse":29,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and knows God. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Jn 2:29","book":"1Jn","chapter":2,"verse":29}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The one who does not love does not know God, because God is love. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"God’s love was revealed among us "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or in us"},{"kind":"text","text":" in this way: God sent "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 9:37","book":"Mrk","chapter":9,"verse":37,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" his one and only Son "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 1:14","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 1:18","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":18,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 3:16","book":"Jhn","chapter":3,"verse":16,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 3:18","book":"Jhn","chapter":3,"verse":18,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" into the world so that we might live "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 10:28","book":"Jhn","chapter":10,"verse":28,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" through him. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 9:37","book":"Mrk","chapter":9,"verse":37},{"label":"Jn 1:14","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":14},{"label":"Jn 1:18","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":18},{"label":"Jn 3:16","book":"Jhn","chapter":3,"verse":16},{"label":"Jn 3:18","book":"Jhn","chapter":3,"verse":18},{"label":"Jn 10:28","book":"Jhn","chapter":10,"verse":28}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or in us"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Love consists in this: not that we loved God, but that he loved us "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 3:16","book":"Jhn","chapter":3,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and sent his Son to be the atoning sacrifice "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or the propitiation"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 5:21","book":"2Co","chapter":5,"verse":21,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 2:2","book":"1Jn","chapter":2,"verse":2,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" for our sins. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 3:16","book":"Jhn","chapter":3,"verse":16},{"label":"2Co 5:21","book":"2Co","chapter":5,"verse":21},{"label":"1Jn 2:2","book":"1Jn","chapter":2,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Or the propitiation"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Dear friends, if God loved us in this way, we also must love one another. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 13:14","book":"Jhn","chapter":13,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 15:12","book":"Jhn","chapter":15,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 13:8","book":"Rom","chapter":13,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 4:9","book":"1Th","chapter":4,"verse":9,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 1:22","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":22,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 13:14","book":"Jhn","chapter":13,"verse":14},{"label":"Jn 15:12","book":"Jhn","chapter":15,"verse":12},{"label":"Rm 13:8","book":"Rom","chapter":13,"verse":8},{"label":"1Th 4:9","book":"1Th","chapter":4,"verse":9},{"label":"1Pt 1:22","book":"1Pe","chapter":1,"verse":22}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"No one has ever seen God. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 33:20","book":"Exo","chapter":33,"verse":20,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" If we love one another, God remains in "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Or remains among"},{"kind":"text","text":" us and his love is made complete in us. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 33:20","book":"Exo","chapter":33,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[{"marker":3,"text":"Or remains among"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"This is how we know that we remain in him "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 15:4–7","book":"Jhn","chapter":15,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 2:6","book":"1Jn","chapter":2,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 2:24","book":"1Jn","chapter":2,"verse":24,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 2:27","book":"1Jn","chapter":2,"verse":27,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 3:6","book":"1Jn","chapter":3,"verse":6,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 3:24","book":"1Jn","chapter":3,"verse":24,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Jn 4:15–16","book":"1Jn","chapter":4,"verse":15,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" and he in us: He has given us of his Spirit. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 3:22","book":"Rev","chapter":3,"verse":22,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 15:4–7","book":"Jhn","chapter":15,"verse":4},{"label":"1Jn 2:6","book":"1Jn","chapter":2,"verse":6},{"label":"1Jn 2:24","book":"1Jn","chapter":2,"verse":24},{"label":"1Jn 2:27","book":"1Jn","chapter":2,"verse":27},{"label":"1Jn 3:6","book":"1Jn","chapter":3,"verse":6},{"label":"1Jn 3:24","book":"1Jn","chapter":3,"verse":24},{"label":"1Jn 4:15–16","book":"1Jn","chapter":4,"verse":15},{"label":"Rv 3:22","book":"Rev","chapter":3,"verse":22}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And we have seen and we testify that the Father has sent his Son "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:3","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" as the world’s Savior. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 1:3","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Whoever confesses "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 9:22","book":"Jhn","chapter":9,"verse":22,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 2:6","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" that Jesus is the Son of God —God remains in him and he in God. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 9:22","book":"Jhn","chapter":9,"verse":22},{"label":"Php 2:6","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And we have come to know and to believe the love that God has for us."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Jn:4:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"In this, love is made complete with us so that we may have confidence in the day of judgment, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 10:15","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 11:22","book":"Mat","chapter":11,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 11:24","book":"Mat","chapter":11,"verse":24,"letter":"c"},